210
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:49,950
where the lights are on,

211
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,950
waiting for me to come back.

212
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:53,700
Alright,

213
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,450
let me add something.

214
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:56,160
What are you doing? Don't mess it up.

215
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:59,660
I'm adding some lights at the door,

216
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:02,790
so no matter how late you get home,

217
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:05,700
it'll light your way.

218
