251
00:16:22,450 --> 00:16:23,750
Chu.

252
00:16:25,450 --> 00:16:28,660
You ungrateful woman.

253
00:16:29,540 --> 00:16:32,790
Have you left me

254
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:36,080
