256
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:45,160
Really, really happy?

257
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:47,160
Yeah?

258
00:17:01,410 --> 00:17:02,700
Sheng Shi.

259
00:17:06,450 --> 00:17:07,410
Are you drunk again?

260
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:08,790
Acting crazy?

261
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:12,250
You're home.

262
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:17,000
