298
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:32,910
Chu.

299
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:42,500
Fanhua,

300
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:44,370
don't you think Shwenny has been

301
00:19:44,450 --> 00:19:46,120
acting a little weird lately?

302
00:19:58,910 --> 00:20:00,450
Do you know

303
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:02,950
