but can't get funding.

307
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:12,450
Everyone who used to be
close to the Han family

308
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:13,660
is ignoring him now.

309
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,160
He's working on a clothing rental app,

310
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:17,160
