311
00:20:17,450 --> 00:20:18,790
Do you have the app?

312
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:20,040
Let me see it.

313
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,120
Yeah.

314
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:29,450
Lanshan,

315
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:30,950
while you were away,

316
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,120
I had Ye Si

317
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:33,450
