318
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:36,160
for our weekly Q&A.

319
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:38,950
He just confirmed.

320
00:20:39,580 --> 00:20:40,200
Could you

321
00:20:40,330 --> 00:20:42,080
draft some interview questions?

322
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:43,870
We can discuss them later.

323
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,250
What's up?

324
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,580
Are you daydreaming?

325
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:54,660
Got it.

326
00:20:54,870 --> 00:20:55,870
Lanshan,

327
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,290
Beiyang Group

328
00:20:57,450 --> 00:20:59,910
is one of the top companies in the city,

329
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,580
with operations

330
00:21:01,870 --> 00:21:03,540
all over the world.

331
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:05,410
Their CEO

332
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:06,750
is rarely in the country.

333
00:21:06,870 --> 00:21:08,620
He's mysterious.

334
00:21:09,330 --> 00:21:12,200
But I heard he's back now.

335
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:15,700
You want him for a live interview?

336
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:18,200
You always know what I'm thinking.

337
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:20,000
Got it.

338
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:22,040
I'll go see him.

339
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,450
Good luck.

340
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:33,910
You know,

341
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:36,040
Chengchi's app is actually interesting.

342
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:37,250
Check this out.

343
00:21:37,410 --> 00:21:39,290
There are quite a few styles available.

344
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:40,870
Not bad.

345
00:21:42,410 --> 00:21:43,410
Look at this one.

346
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,160
It's really nice.

347
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:46,500
It is.

348
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:49,770
Hello.

349
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:51,410
Hello, Director Li.

350
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:52,790
Come to my office.

351
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:57,040
Why are you calling the CFO?

352
00:22:06,410 --> 00:22:07,830
Mr. Sheng, you wanted to see me?

353
00:22:08,290 --> 00:22:10,120
How much money
do we have available right now?

354
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,790
We've got 200 million we can access.

355
00:22:12,910 --> 00:22:14,540
Another 3 billion is tied up

356
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:16,450
for the project bids.

357
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:18,660
Fanhua,

358
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:22,160
draft a venture capital agreement
for 100 million.

359
00:22:22,620 --> 00:22:23,700
For Chengchi?

360
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:26,330
Mr. Sheng,

361
00:22:26,450 --> 00:22:27,120
we've got a 100 million payment due

362
00:22:27,290 --> 00:22:29,080
for the project renovation in two days.

363
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:30,040
If we do this,

364
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:32,000
we won't have any cash left.

365
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,790
Just do what I said.

366
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,200
Alright.

367
00:22:41,410 --> 00:22:42,410
Shwenny,

368
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:43,790
is this really necessary?

369
00:22:45,410 --> 00:22:48,580
I just want to make sure
that person's taken care of.

370
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:55,660
Why does he still want Chengchi

371
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:57,200
to be taken care of?

372
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,870
Editor Gu.

373
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:23,830
Hello.

374
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:25,450
Yes, and you are?

375
00:23:25,540 --> 00:23:26,290
I'm Chu Peng.

376
00:23:26,410 --> 00:23:28,290
We met in Peng City when I was painting.

377
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,080
Remember me?

378
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:32,540
I like to wander around

379
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:33,620
and experience

380
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,290
different things in life.

381
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:36,540
Who knew

382
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:39,290
we'd cross paths again?

383
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:40,580
Mr. Chu,

384
00:23:40,700 --> 00:23:42,160
last time you gave me a painting,

385
00:23:42,330 --> 00:23:44,410
I thought you were an artist.
I didn't realize...

386
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:45,500
Life is

387
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:46,830
full of surprises.

388
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:48,620
The unknown is what

389
00:23:48,700 --> 00:23:49,950
makes it exciting,

390
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:52,620
