393
00:23:57,660 --> 00:24:00,000
I prefer a quieter life.

394
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:02,450
Mr. Chu,

395
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:04,370
I really liked the painting you gave me.

396
00:24:04,450 --> 00:24:05,250
Thank you.

397
00:24:05,910 --> 00:24:07,160
Do you also paint?

398
00:24:07,330 --> 00:24:09,450
I often paint alone.

399
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:11,290
I'm not very good,

400
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:13,830
but it brings me peace

401
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:14,910
and helps me

402
00:24:14,950 --> 00:24:16,450
