on our magazine's weekly Q&A.

407
00:24:24,950 --> 00:24:25,950
I'd love to.

408
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:12,700
Shwenny.

409
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:14,660
What brings you here?

410
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,200
How much do you need?

411
00:25:21,580 --> 00:25:22,830
At least 50 million.

412
00:25:37,180 --> 00:25:39,310
[Investment: 100 million RMB]

413
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:40,540
Shwenny,

414
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,160
