415
00:25:42,250 --> 00:25:43,080
Not enough?

416
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:53,410
It'll do.

417
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:54,700
Alright.

418
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:56,950
If you're okay with it,

419
00:25:57,040 --> 00:25:58,040
